<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ basics.name }} - Cover Letter</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Merriweather:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c3e50;
            --text-color: #333333;
            --light-text: #666666;
            --link-color: #2980b9;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text-color);
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* Header / Letterhead */
        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.2em;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .contact-info {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            color: var(--light-text);
        }

        .contact-separator {
            margin: 0 8px;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        a {
            color: var(--link-color);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Letter Content */
        .meta-info {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .date {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .recipient {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .subject {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .content ul {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .signature-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>{{ basics.name }}</h1>
        <div class="contact-info">
            {{ basics.location }}
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            {{ basics.phone }}
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            <a href="mailto:{{ basics.email }}">{{ basics.email }}</a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-info">
            <a href="https://{{ basics.linkedin }}">LinkedIn</a>
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            <a href="https://{{ basics.github }}">GitHub</a>
            <span class="contact-separator">|</span>
            <a href="https://{{ basics.portfolio }}">Portfolio</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="meta-info">
        <div class="date">{{ date }}</div>
        <div class="recipient">Hiring Manager</div>
        <div class="subject">Re: Application for {{ role_title }} Position</div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear Hiring Manager,</p>

        <p>I am writing to express my strong interest in the {{ role_title }} position. As a {{ basics.label }} with a background in {{ background_context }}, I am excited about the opportunity to contribute to your team's security posture.</p>

        <p>{{ summary }}</p>

        <p>In my recent work, I have focused heavily on practical, hands-on security operations:</p>
        <ul>
            {% for project in projects[:2] %}
            <li>
                <strong>
                    {% if project.url %}
                    <a href="{{ project.url }}" target="_blank">{{ project.title }}</a>
                    {% else %}
                    {{ project.title }}
                    {% endif %}
                </strong>: {{ project.bullets[0] }}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>

        <p>My technical foundation in {{ skills.security_tools[:3]|join(', ') }} and {{ skills.programming[:2]|join(', ') }} allows me to bridge the gap between theoretical security concepts and real-world implementation. I am particularly drawn to this role because it aligns with my passion for proactive defense and continuous improvement.</p>

        <p>I would welcome the opportunity to discuss how my skills and experience align with your needs. Thank you for your time and consideration.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature">
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <div class="signature-name">{{ basics.name }}</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
